\c 13 Kutadza kwaAmoni 1 Zvino shure kwaizvozvo Abhusaromu mwanakomana waDhavhidhi wakanga ane hanzvadzi yakanaka, wainzi Tamari; Amoni mwanakomana waDhavhidhi akamuda. 2 Amoni akatambudzika, akarwara pamusoro paTamari hanzvadzi yake; nokuti yakanga iri rnhandara, Amoni akaona kuti haangamuiti chinhu. 3 Asi Amoni wakanga ane shamwari, yainzi Jonadhabhu mwanakomana waShimei, mukoma waDhavhidhi; zvino Jonadhabhu wakanga ari munhu waiva namano. 4 Iye akati kwaari, "Nhandi, mwanakomana wamambo, wakawondereiko kudai mazuva ose? Haungandiudzi here?" Amoni akati kwaari, "Ndinoda Tamari, hanzvadzi yomunun'una wangu Abhusaromu." 5 Jonadhabhu akati kwaari, "Vata panhoo dzako, uzviite somunhu unorwara; z.v.mo kaw kn.bia vako Nakasvika. kuzo - kuona, uti kwavari, `Ndinokumbira kuti hanzvadzi yangu Tamari auye, andipe zvokudya, ndidye, agadzire zvokudya pamberi pangu, ndizviwone, ndizvidye pamaoko ake.' "
